decks.notes: This deck focuses on utilizing efficient creatures and disruption spells to apply pressure on the opponent early in the game. By utilizing cards like Collected Company and Luminarch Aspirant, it aims to quickly build a board presence and overwhelm the opponent with aggressive plays. Additionally, the inclusion of cards like Thalia, Heretic Cathar and Archon of Emeria disrupt the opponent's game plan, making it difficult for them to effectively respond to the aggressive threats on the board. Overall, this deck aims to quickly establish dominance and close out the game before the opponent can stabilize.
